Markdown# hxd — tiny & fast hex viewer in C

[![CI](https://github.com/jjice/hxd/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/jjice/hxd/actions)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)

